        "info": "QR Code Link to This Post Brush Meadows I - A place to call home! Bed: 2 / Bath: 1 Sq. Footage: 905 sq ft Monthly Price: $1361 - $1446 *Optional and usage-based charges not included. Contact office to confirm pricing details and included fees. Terms: 12-Month Contact us for more information! show contact info At Brush Meadows, we've designed every detail in and around our one, two, and three-bedroom apartments with a fulfilling experience in mind. Our homes for rent are filled with ideal features, including a dishwasher, a private patio or balcony, air conditioning, and more. Where you live matters just as much as how you live. In addition to our great home features, we have filled our community with an abundance of amenities for you to enjoy. Take advantage of our playground, basketball court, beautiful grounds, and much more. $500 Off Move-in special, waived application fee Our Apartment Homes Feature: ● Bathtub/Shower ● Blinds ● Carpeting ● Dishwasher ● Extra Storage ● W/D Hookups ● Washer & Dryer Connections ● Washer Dryer Hookup ● Wheelchair Accessible (Rooms) ● Wired for Cable Our Residents Enjoy: ● Basketball Court ● BBQ Area ● Bike Racks ● Emergency Maintenance ● Garages ● Pet Friendly ● Pets Allowed ● Playground ● Smoke Free ● Some Paid Utilities Contact us for more information! show contact info 1203 Lake Elmo Dr Billings, MT 59105 Website: www.apts-rental.com?n=brush_meadows_i&rp=ionmEbnkRTGx&t=wb Schedule a Tour: www.apts-rental.com?n=brush_meadows_i&rp=ionmEbnkRTGx&t=sch Mon - Fri: 8:00 AM - 5:00 PM Sat - Sun: - Pets: Pets Welcome! Non-aggressive breeds accepted. Weight Restrictions may apply. Please see the office for fees & other details! CALL OFFICE FOR AVAILABILITY *Image shown is for demonstration purposes only & may not be an exact representation of the product.* All pricing, availability, fees, and terms are subject to change without notice. EQUAL HOUSING OPPORTUNITY 7VR8ZRHHRL1A396",
