        "description": "QR Code Link to This Post Brush Meadows I Leasing Office: 1203 Lake Elmo Dr Billings, MT 59105 Call us at show contact info Take a look at what Brush Meadows I has to offer! At Brush Meadows, we've designed every detail in and around our one, two, and three-bedroom apartments with a fulfilling experience in mind. Our homes for rent are filled with ideal features, including a dishwasher, a private patio or balcony, air conditioning, and more. Where you live matters just as much as how you live. In addition to our great home features, we have filled our community with an abundance of amenities for you to enjoy. Take advantage of our playground, basketball court, beautiful grounds, and much more. $500.00 Off Move-in Costs, Waived application fee Rental Information: 3 Bedroom / 1 Bathroom / 1154 sq ft Monthly Price: $1575 *Optional and usage-based charges not included. Contact office to confirm pricing details and included fees. Lease Terms: 12-Month Apartment Amenities: − Air Conditioner − Cable Ready − Ceiling Fan − Dining Area − Energy Efficient Appliances − Heating − Patio/Balcony In select units − Walk-In Showers − Window Coverings − Wood Like Flooring Additional Information: − Basketball Court − Covered Parking − Garages − Laundry Facilities − Playground − RentPlus Leasing Hours: Mon - Fri: 8:00 AM - 5:00 PM Sat - Sun: - Call us at show contact info Pet Policy: Pets Welcome! Non-aggressive breeds accepted. Weight Restrictions may apply. Please see the office for fees & other details! Website: www.apts-rental.com?n=brush_meadows_i&rp=rhbQyQ8o3txo&t=wb Online Application: www.apts-rental.com?n=brush_meadows_i&rp=rhbQyQ8o3txo&t=ap Schedule a Tour: www.apts-rental.com?n=brush_meadows_i&rp=rhbQyQ8o3txo&t=sch CALL OFFOCE FOR AVAILABILITY *Image shown is for demonstration purposes only & may not be an exact representation of the product.* All pricing, availability, fees, and terms are subject to change without notice. EQUAL HOUSING OPPORTUNITY 13L