        "description": "QR Code Link to This Post Shiloh Glen Address: 3900 Olympic Blvd Billings, MT 59102 Monthly Price: $1065 *Optional and usage-based charges not included. Contact office to confirm pricing details and included fees. Bedrooms: Studio | Baths: 1 | Sq. Footage: 502 sq ft | Terms: 6-Month, 7-Month, 8-Month, 9-Month, 10-Month, 11-Month, 12-Month Call us today at show contact info + + + + + + + + + + + + + + + + + + + + + + + + + + + + + + + + + + + + + + + + + + + + + + + Features in this apartment home: ● Carpet ● Deck ● Dining Room ● Dishwasher ● Kitchen ● Oven ● Patio ● Range ● Refrigerator/Freezer ● Views ● Air Conditioning ● Cable Ready ● Vinyl Flooring ● Walk-in closet in select homes ● Wheelchair Accessible (Rooms) ● Window Coverings + + + + + + + + + + + + + + + + + + + + + + + + + + + + + + + + + + + + + + + + + + + + + + + Amenities at our property: ● Brand-new playground ● Garages available ● Lawn ● Maintenance on site ● Outdoor Entry ● Playground ● Porch ● Private Mailboxes ● Resident Manager ● Smoke-Free ● After Hour Lighting ● After Hour Maintenance ● Close to Parks ● Close to Public Transportation ● Close to Restaurants ● Close to Schools ● Close to Shopping ● On-Site Leasing Office ● Storage Space + + + + + + + + + + + + + + + + + + + + + + + + + + + + + + + + + + + + + + + + + + + + + + + About the community: Shiloh Glen offers a peaceful setting with all the conveniences of the city. Enjoy being close to parks and trails and just across the street from some of the best dining and shopping in Billings. The property is just a short drive from the airport and the premier Shiloh Crossing Shopping Center, where new retail and restaurants are continually added. Choose from spacious studio, one-, two- and three- bedroom floor plans featuring air conditioning and patio or deck with storage. As a resident, you will enjoy great amenities including a laundry center, outdoor picnic area, and brand-new playground. Find out more and let us help you find your new home today! Pets: 2 pets max per home, $50 pet rent per pet, $400 refundable deposit per pet, Call for breed restrictions Call us today at show contact info Hours: Mon - Fri: 8:30 AM - 4:30 PM Saturday Closed. Sunday Closed. Facebook: https://www.facebook.com/Shilohglenapartments/?rcstdid=MzM%3D-dkCsfkCKtXI%3D Website: www.rentalsapts.com?n=shiloh_glen&rp=6vn7e3ebfaMg&t=wb Online Application: www.rentalsapts.com?n=shiloh_glen&rp=6vn7e3ebfaMg&t=ap Schedule a Tour: www.rentalsapts.com?n=shiloh_glen&rp=6vn7e3ebfaMg&t=sch All pricing, availability, fees, and terms are subject to change without notice. EQUAL HOUSING OPPORTUNITY 7D80D50BAC074C7",
