        "description": "QR Code Link to This Post Brush Meadows I - A place to call home! Bed: 3 / Bath: 1 Sq. Footage: 1154 sq ft Monthly Price: $1575 *Optional and usage-based charges not included. Contact office to confirm pricing details and included fees. Terms: 12-Month Phone Number: show contact info At Brush Meadows, we've designed every detail in and around our one, two, and three-bedroom apartments with a fulfilling experience in mind. Our homes for rent are filled with ideal features, including a dishwasher, a private patio or balcony, air conditioning, and more. Where you live matters just as much as how you live. In addition to our great home features, we have filled our community with an abundance of amenities for you to enjoy. Take advantage of our playground, basketball court, beautiful grounds, and much more. $500.00 Off Move-in Costs, Waived application fee Our Apartment Homes Feature: ◾ Air Conditioner ◾ Bathtub/Shower ◾ Breakfast Bar ◾ Cable Ready ◾ Dining Area ◾ Dishwasher ◾ Heating ◾ Linen Closet ◾ Patio/Balcony In select units ◾ Wheelchair access Our Residents Enjoy: ◾ Basketball Court ◾ Covered Parking ◾ Garages ◾ Laundry Facilities ◾ Playground ◾ RentPlus Phone Number: show contact info 1225 Lake Elmo Dr Billings, MT 59105 Website: www.lease-apts.com?n=brush_meadows_i&rp=h7bCaV5LXJtw&t=wb Online Application: www.lease-apts.com?n=brush_meadows_i&rp=h7bCaV5LXJtw&t=ap Schedule a Tour: www.lease-apts.com?n=brush_meadows_i&rp=h7bCaV5LXJtw&t=sch Mon - Fri: 9:00 AM - 5:00 PM Pets: Pets Welcome! Non-aggressive breeds accepted. Weight Restrictions may apply. Please see the office for fees & other details! CALL OFFOCE FOR AVAILABILITY *Image shown is for demonstration purposes only & may not be an exact representation of the product.* All pricing, availability, fees, and terms are subject to change without notice. EQUAL HOUSING OPPORTUNITY 13L1ZJ1M6Z2N4MM",
