        "description": "QR Code Link to This Post Brush Meadows I 1203 Lake Elmo Dr Billings, MT 59105 Monthly Price: $1368 *Optional and usage-based charges not included. Contact office to confirm pricing details and included fees. Bedrooms: 2 Bathrooms: 1 Square Footage: 761 sq ft Reach out via phone: show contact info $500.00 Off Move-in costs, waived application fee Features in this apartment home: − Air Conditioner − Dishwasher − Patio/Balcony In select units − W/D Hookup In select units − Wheelchair access About the community: At Brush Meadows, we've designed every detail in and around our one, two, and three-bedroom apartments with a fulfilling experience in mind. Our homes for rent are filled with ideal features, including a dishwasher, a private patio or balcony, air conditioning, and more. Where you live matters just as much as how you live. In addition to our great home features, we have filled our community with an abundance of amenities for you to enjoy. Take advantage of our playground, basketball court, beautiful grounds, and much more. Amenities at our property: − Affordable Housing − Basketball Court − Bike Racks − Emergency Maintenance − Garages − Green Community − Laundry Facilities − Lawn − Pet Friendly − Some Paid Utilities Additional information: Reach out via phone: show contact info Terms: 12-Month Pets: Pets Welcome! Non-aggressive breeds accepted. Weight Restrictions may apply. Please see the office for fees & other details! Website: www.lease-apts.com?n=brush_meadows_i&rp=4exGyBzwjLqL&t=wb Schedule a Tour: www.lease-apts.com?n=brush_meadows_i&rp=4exGyBzwjLqL&t=sch CALL OFFOCE FOR AVAILABILITY *Image shown is for demonstration purposes only & may not be an exact representation of the product.* All pricing, availability, fees, and terms are subject to change without notice. EQUAL HOUSING OPPORTUNITY JK3VM922SHVS386",
