        "geocode_query": "3900 Olympic Blvd near King Ave W/Shiloh Rd, Billings",
        "description": "QR Code Link to This Post Welcome to Shiloh Glen Rental Information Monthly Price: $1695 - $1795 *Optional and usage-based charges not included. Contact office to confirm pricing details and included fees. 3 Bedroom 2 Bath | 1117 sq ft Lease Term: 6-Month, 7-Month, 8-Month, 9-Month, 10-Month, 11-Month, 12-Month Call for details: show contact info Apartment Amenities ✓ Carpet ✓ Deck ✓ Dining Room ✓ Dishwasher ✓ Kitchen ✓ Oven ✓ Patio ✓ Range ✓ Refrigerator/Freezer ✓ Views ✓ Air Conditioning ✓ Cable Ready ✓ Vinyl Flooring ✓ Walk-in closet in select homes ✓ Wheelchair Accessible (Rooms) ✓ Window Coverings Community Features ✓ Brand-new playground ✓ Garages available ✓ Laundry Facilities ✓ Lawn ✓ Maintenance on site ✓ Outdoor Entry ✓ Playground ✓ Porch ✓ Resident Manager ✓ Smoke-Free ✓ After Hour Lighting ✓ After Hour Maintenance ✓ Close to Parks ✓ Close to Public Transportation ✓ Close to Restaurants ✓ Close to Schools ✓ Close to Shopping ✓ On-Site Leasing Office ✓ Storage Space About Community Description: Shiloh Glen offers a peaceful setting with all the conveniences of the city. Enjoy being close to parks and trails and just across the street from some of the best dining and shopping in Billings. The property is just a short drive from the airport and the premier Shiloh Crossing Shopping Center, where new retail and restaurants are continually added. Choose from spacious studio, one-, two- and three- bedroom floor plans featuring air conditioning and patio or deck with storage. As a resident, you will enjoy great amenities including a laundry center, outdoor picnic area, and brand-new playground. Find out more and let us help you find your new home today! Location: 3900 Olympic Blvd Billings, MT 59102 show contact info Office Hours: Mon - Fri: 8:30 AM - 4:30 PM Saturday Closed. Sunday Closed. Additional Information Call for details: show contact info Pet Policy: 2 pets max per home, $50 pet rent per pet, $400 refundable deposit per pet, Call for breed restrictions Facebook: https://www.facebook.com/Shilohglenapartments/?rcstdid=MzM%3D-dkCsfkCKtXI%3D Website: www.rentalsapts.com?n=shiloh_glen&rp=tAEYXJtPQmhe&t=wb Online Application: www.rentalsapts.com?n=shiloh_glen&rp=tAEYXJtPQmhe&t=ap Schedule a Tour: www.rentalsapts.com?n=shiloh_glen&rp=tAEYXJtPQmhe&t=sch All pricing, availability, fees, and terms are subject to change without notice. EQUAL HOUSING OPPORTUNITY CFBBB4B89278496",
