        "info": "QR Code Link to This Post 4 Bed (1 non-egress) High End Home in Billings Heights Property Address 681 Garnet Avenue | Billings, MT 59105 Available: 07/01/2026 Offered By Debizel Property Managers Description This four bedroom, two and a half bathroom Heights home offers all the amenities that one would expect in a high end home! The entryway is large and inviting and leads to one of the living areas, complete with a gas fireplace. The half bath and laundry are also on this level. The updated kitchen with granite counter tops opens onto the formal dining room and another living area. Upstairs there are three generous bedrooms including a primary suite and a large full bathroom. The lower level has one non-egress bedroom and plenty of storage. All of this plus a 2 car attached garage, central air, underground sprinklers, an enormous privacy-fenced back yard and a wonderful deck perfect for your barbecue parties in the summer! **Updated Photos Coming Soon!** Debizel Property Managers is an Equal Opportunity Housing Provider Amenities Dishwasher Fenced Yard 2 Car Garage Tenant Pays All Utilities Formal Dining Area Family Room Master Suite A/C Gas Fireplace No Smoking Renter's Insurance Required Deck Lots of Storage Washer/Dryer Hookups Granite Countertops Details Beds/Baths: 4BD/2.5BA Square Feet: 2,799 Rental Terms Rent: $2,295.00 Available: 07/01/2026 Application Fee: $27.00 Security Deposit: $2,295.00",
