        "description": "QR Code Link to This Post 2-Bedroom Lower Level Apartment Near the Moss Mansion Property Address 109 Yellowstone - 107 Yellowstone | Billings, MT 59101 Available: Now Offered By Debizel Property Managers Description You'll love this large and bright 2-bedroom lower-level apartment in the beautiful historic district of Billings, near the Moss Mansion and downtown. There are both a front and backyard entrance and a single detached garage off the alley that comes with this rental. Tenant has their own gas and electric meters and also pays 2/5 of the monthly City of Billings Public Utilities bill. Walking distance to downtown and schools. There is a large shared laundry room, but you have your own hook-ups. The yard is shared with the upstairs tenant. Non-smoking house and premises. Renters insurance is required. Debizel Property Managers is an Equal Opportunity Housing Provider Amenities Dining Area Tenant Pays All Utilities No Smoking Renter's Insurance Required Washer/Dryer Hookups Off Street Parking Up / Down Duplex Lower Level Unit Detached Single Car Garage Details Beds/Baths: 2BD/1.0BA Rental Terms Rent: $1,050.00 Available: Now Application Fee: $27.00 Security Deposit: $1,050.00",
