        "msg": "QR Code Link to This Post West-end rental with private backyard patio 2981 Ave. E, Billings, MT 59102 1995.00 / Month 3 BEDROOMS | 2 BATHROOMS Interested? Fill out this form : https://renter.turbotenant.com/general-prescreener/T3duZXI6NTg1ODIx?property=1097290&source=cl Have questions? Contact the Landlord : https://rental.turbotenant.com/p/2981-ave.-e-billings-mt/6a871e1b-10e0-4211-9575-ae2a1e5d5e34?source=craigslist Property Description: Great rental located in Billings West End in a great neighborhood. This is a 3 bedroom with 2 upstairs bedrooms and 1 bedroom downstairs. It has 2 bathrooms, spacious kitchen, dining area, single car heated garage, and large private patio in backyard for enjoying summer days with friends and family. Laundry hook-ups and central air. Great location on the west end within walking distance of grocery store, coffee shop, gyms, schools, and restaurants. Located near walking / bike path. No pets for this rental. $1995.00/month + gas and electric. Water and internet paid by landlord. If you would like to schedule a showing, complete the pre-screen questionnaire and indicate when you are available for tour. I will reach out by text or phone to arrange showing. The prescreen will be sent to you via email &/or text about expressing interest to rental. Schools: Poly Drive Elementary (1 mile), Will James Middle School (0.5 miles), Senior (school bus available) Property Type : Pets : No Pets Allowed Smoking : NO Lease Term : 1995.00 / Month 1600.00 Deposit Lease Length: One Year Available: 07/06/2026 Occupancy Limit: No Limit Utilities Included : Water Garbage Sewage Internet Appliances : Dishwasher Refrigerator Range Oven Amenities : Near Parks Lawn Washer Dryer Hookups Garage Heating & Cooling : Forced Air Central Interested? Fill out this form : https://renter.turbotenant.com/general-prescreener/T3duZXI6NTg1ODIx?property=1097290&source=cl Have questions? Contact the Landlord : https://rental.turbotenant.com/p/2981-ave.-e-bil