        "description": "QR Code Link to This Post Fully Furnished Split Level Two-Bedroom Home Property Address 1019 N 24th Street | Billings, MT 59101 Available: Now Offered By Debizel Property Managers Description This fully furnished, split-level two-bedroom, two-bath home offers separated living spaces upstairs and in the basement, giving you flexibility and room to spread out. Its a great setup for anyone who appreciates having distinct areas for relaxing and sleeping. Both bedrooms feature queen beds, creating a consistent, comfortable feel throughout. The primary bedroom connects to a bathroom with a bathtub and shower combo that is also accessible from the main part of the house. Downstairs, the basement includes a walk-in shower and a den-style living space with oversized chairs, offering a second lounge area that feels tucked away and private. The full kitchen is equipped with a dishwasher and everything you need for everyday cooking, and laundry facilities are available on-site for added convenience. The dining room opens onto a back deck, making it easy to step outside for fresh air or a quiet evening. The large, fenced backyard provides additional outdoor space to enjoy, along with a set of chairs for relaxing. With its walkable access to both hospitals and close proximity to the airport and downtown, this home offers a practical and comfortable place to settle in. This unit offers a month to month lease with a minimum stay of one month, all utilities are included with the monthly rent and there is a $150 cleaning fee for the unit. Debizel Property Managers is an Equal Opportunity Housing Provider Amenities Dishwasher Microwave A/C No Smoking Stainless Steel Appliances All Utilities Included Open Floor Plan Wifi Included Back Deck Updated Kitchen Washer / Dryer Provided Month to Month Lease Fully Fenced Yard Essentials (Kitchenware Bathware Linens) Full-size ironing board Hair Dryer Smart TV Internet Free Parking on Premesis Full-Size Fridge Room Darken