        "description": "QR Code Link to This Post Shiloh Glen 3900 Olympic Blvd Billings, MT 59102 A wonderful home in Billings is waiting for you! Office Phone: show contact info We currently have a gorgeous Studio bedroom 1 bathroom with 502 sq ft. Monthly Price: $1025 *Optional and usage-based charges not included. Contact office to confirm pricing details and included fees. Shiloh Glen offers a peaceful setting with all the conveniences of the city. Enjoy being close to parks and trails and just across the street from some of the best dining and shopping in Billings. The property is just a short drive from the airport and the premier Shiloh Crossing Shopping Center, where new retail and restaurants are continually added. Choose from spacious studio, one-, two- and three- bedroom floor plans featuring air conditioning and patio or deck with storage. As a resident, you will enjoy great amenities including a laundry center, outdoor picnic area, and brand-new playground. Find out more and let us help you find your new home today! Community Highlights: ● Garages available ● Laundry Facilities ● Lawn ● Maintenance on site ● Outdoor Entry ● Playground ● Porch ● Private Mailboxes ● Reserved parking ● Resident Manager ● After Hour Lighting ● After Hour Maintenance ● Close to Parks ● Close to Public Transportation ● Close to Restaurants ● Close to Schools ● Close to Shopping ● On-Site Leasing Office ● Storage Space Apartment Home Highlights: ● Carpet ● Deck ● Dining Room ● Dishwasher ● Kitchen ● Oven ● Patio ● Range ● Refrigerator/Freezer ● Views ● Air Conditioning ● Cable Ready ● Vinyl Flooring ● Walk-in closet in select homes ● Wheelchair Accessible (Rooms) ● Window Coverings Office Phone: show contact info Facebook: https://www.facebook.com/Shilohglenapartments/?rcstdid=MzM%3D-dkCsfkCKtXI%3D Website: www.lease-apts.com?n=shiloh_glen&rp=xnKyw5JDJdoa&t=wb Online Application: www.lease-apts.com?n=shiloh_glen&rp=xnKyw5JDJdoa&t=ap Schedule a Tour: www.lease-apts.com?n=shilo