        "msg": "QR Code Link to This Post Brush Meadows I Visit our community today! 1203 Lake Elmo Dr Billings, MT 59105 Office Phone: show contact info $500 Off Move-in costs, waived application fee Monthly Price: $1368 *Optional and usage-based charges not included. Contact office to confirm pricing details and included fees. Apartment Type: 2-BR 1-BA Apartment Size: 761 sq ft Lease Terms: 12-Month Pet Policy: Pets Welcome! Non-aggressive breeds accepted. Weight Restrictions may apply. Please see the office for fees & other details! What you'll find in our community: ✓ BBQ Area ✓ Bike Racks ✓ Detached Garage(s) ✓ Garage(s) ✓ On-line Maintenance Request ✓ On-Line Payments ✓ Pets Allowed ✓ Playground ✓ RentPlus ✓ Some Paid Utilities Description: At Brush Meadows, we've designed every detail in and around our one, two, and three-bedroom apartments with a fulfilling experience in mind. Our homes for rent are filled with ideal features, including a dishwasher, a private patio or balcony, air conditioning, and more. Where you live matters just as much as how you live. In addition to our great home features, we have filled our community with an abundance of amenities for you to enjoy. Take advantage of our playground, basketball court, beautiful grounds, and much more. This apartment comes with: ✓ Air Conditioner ✓ Dishwasher ✓ Patio/Balcony In select units ✓ W/D Hookup In select units ✓ Wheelchair access Office Phone: show contact info Mon - Fri: 8:00 AM - 5:00 PM Sat - Sun: - Visit our website to schedule a personal tour! Website: www.rentalsapts.com?n=brush_meadows_i&rp=up5x3cVcPoxq&t=wb Schedule a Tour: www.rentalsapts.com?n=brush_meadows_i&rp=up5x3cVcPoxq&t=sch CALL OFFOCE FOR AVAILABILITY *Image shown is for demonstration purposes only & may not be an exact representation of the product.* All pricing, availability, fees, and terms are subject to change without notice. EQUAL HOUSING OPPORTUNITY 5RM89SLJ5O5137O",
