        "msg": "QR Code Link to This Post A beautifully remodeled two bedroom/one bath home will be available on May 1st. This cozy home is 750 sqft, has hardwood floors throughout, new kitchen appliances and under-counter/low-key lighting. Washer/dryer hookups, a small patio for your BBQ, and an outdoor storage shed make this a perfect home for a small family or medical professionals who need to be close to the hospitals. Surrounded by mature trees, it’s located on a quiet street one block away from Central Park. Grocery shopping is very close and so is downtown. It features off street parking, a front yard, and a fenced back yard that is perfect for your dog. Rent is $1500/month with $3000 deposit ($3300 with a pet). Deposits ARE FULLY REFUNDABLE if the house is returned as clean as you received it. No smoking/drugs. Contact Dave for more information.",
