        "info": "QR Code Link to This Post Modern Single Unit Home in Billings | 44 Redrock Dr | $1700/mo | Available 06/30/2026 44 Redrock Dr, Billings , MT 59102 1700.00 / Month 3 BEDROOMS | 1.5 BATHROOMS Interested? Fill out this form : https://renter.turbotenant.com/general-prescreener/T3duZXI6NTY2MTA2?property=2711964&source=cl Have questions? Contact the Landlord : https://rental.turbotenant.com/p/44-redrock-dr-billings-mt/450a748c-75b2-4886-9e71-900ebb3c6b66?source=craigslist Property Description: Welcome to your new home at 44 Redrock Dr in Billings, MT! This single-unit property offers a spacious layout with modern amenities such as dishwasher, washer/dryer, and more. Enjoy the convenience of off-street parking, secure building, and on-site laundry. Pets are welcome too! Don't miss out on this amazing opportunity - schedule a viewing today! Property Type : Single Family Pets : Small Dogs, Large Dogs, Cats Allowed Smoking : NO Lease Term : 1700.00 / Month 1200.00 Deposit Lease Length: One Year Available: 06/30/2026 Occupancy Limit: 3 People Utilities Included : Sewage Water Garbage Appliances : Dishwasher Range Oven Refrigerator Washer Dryer Amenities : Bicycle Parking Cable Ready Lawn Near Parks Off Street Parking Secure Building On Site Laundry Washer Dryer Hookups Heating & Cooling : Forced Air Wall Interested? Fill out this form : https://renter.turbotenant.com/general-prescreener/T3duZXI6NTY2MTA2?property=2711964&source=cl Have questions? Contact the Landlord : https://rental.turbotenant.com/p/44-redrock-dr-billings-mt/450a748c-75b2-4886-9e71-900ebb3c6b66?source=craigslist",
