        "description": "QR Code Link to This Post Rock Creek Bedroom: 1 - 3 | Bathroom: 1 Square Footage: 645 - 845 sq ft Monthly Price: $1025 - $1570 *Optional and usage-based charges not included. Contact office to confirm pricing details and included fees. Contact: show contact info Community Description \"Currently fully leased. Accepting inquiries for future available units.\" Rock Creek is a recently updated apartment community in Billings, MT. The property is walking distance to Boulder Elementary School, across the street from Boulder Park and only a few blocks from a shopping center and dining options. Inside Rock Creek, residents enjoy spacious living rooms, kitchens, and bathrooms with updated features in select homes, garbage disposals, and great floor plans. Rock Creek is a great place to call home - find out more and let us help you find your new home. Community Amenities ➢ Breakfast Bars ➢ Clubhouse ➢ Fitness Center ➢ Free Storage Locker ➢ Garages Available ➢ Laundry Facility ➢ Online Leases, Work Orders & Rent Payments ➢ Outdoor Patio w/ BBQ & Water Fountain Apartment Features ➢ Breakfast Bars ➢ Custom Cabinetry ➢ Dishwasher ➢ Disposal In Select Units ➢ Large Windows ➢ New Flooring ➢ New Vinyl Windows In Select Units ➢ Spacious Living Areas ➢ Storage Space ➢ Tile Backsplash In Select units Contact Information Visit Us: 2323 32nd St W Billings, MT 59102 Contact: show contact info Hours: Mon - Fri: 8:30 AM - 5:00 PM Facebook: https://www.facebook.com/rockcreekbillings/?rcstdid=MzM%3D-dkCsfkCKtXI%3D Website: www.apts-rental.com?n=rock_creek&rp=cEpTbqc4jsz7&t=wb Online Application: www.apts-rental.com?n=rock_creek&rp=cEpTbqc4jsz7&t=ap Schedule a Tour: www.apts-rental.com?n=rock_creek&rp=cEpTbqc4jsz7&t=sch Additional Details Pet Policy: 2 pets per home Deposit and pet rent apply Breed restrictions apply $50 pet rent Lease Terms: 6-Month, 7-Month, 8-Month, 9-Month, 10-Month, 11-Month, 12-Month All pricing, availability, fees, and terms are subject to change without notice. EQUAL HOUSING OPPORTUNITY AB9EE2A9BE3F471F",
