        "geocode_query": "3-bedroom, 1-bath apartment in Billings",
        "description": "QR Code Link to This Post Furnished 3 Bedroom Near Both Hospitals 1718 Virginia Ln, B, Basement, Billings, MT 59102 1795.00 / Month 1 BEDROOMS | 1 BATHROOMS Interested? Fill out this form : https://renter.turbotenant.com/general-prescreener/T3duZXI6OTIxMTMx?property=2603331&source=cl Have questions? Contact the Landlord : https://rental.turbotenant.com/p/1718-virginia-ln-billings-mt-unit-b/64145766-ca8c-481d-b7a8-9bdc5151352b?source=craigslist Property Description: Furnished, bright, BRAND NEW 3-bedroom, 1-bath apartment in Billings, MT. Walking distance to both hospitals. This residence includes a detached garage and convenient in-unit laundry, plus a dishwasher for easier meal cleanup. The property features a sprinkler system and exterior security cameras, and the landlord handles lawn care. Located across the street from Pioneer Park and close to hospitals and both colleges, it offers practical access to local amenities and institutions. Shared patio and unfenced backyard. We add a flat fee for utilities and include cable internet, so you only have one bill per month. Liability Insurance required. No Pets. Utility fee includes Central A/C, Internet, Smart TV and WiFi access plus gas, water, electricity. Please note: You may schedule a showing before applying. If you need a FaceTime or Google Meet showing, please just ask. Our application platform charges a $35 fee at the time of application. The full amount covers credit and background checks that are run automatically for every applicant. Because these services are performed immediately, there is no refundable portion of the fee under Montana law. Sucasa does not profit from your application fees in any way. Showings happening now; unit available 8/1/26. Property Type : Single Family Pets : No Pets Allowed Smoking : NO Lease Term : 1795.00 / Month 1600.00 Deposit Lease Length: One Year Available: 08/01/2026 Occupancy Limit: 6 People Utilities Included : Cable Internet Sewage Water Gas Electricity Garbage Appliances : Dishwasher Dryer Freezer Microwave Range Oven Refrigerator Washer Amenities : Bicycle Parking Cable Ready Near Parks Lawn Furnished Secure Building Security Cameras Wired For Internet Heating & Cooling : Forced Air Central Interested? Fill out this form : https://renter.turbotenant.com/general-prescreener/T3duZXI6OTIxMTMx?property=2603331&source=cl Have questions? Contact the Landlord : https://rental.turbotenant.com/p/1718-virginia-ln-billings-mt-unit-b/64145766-ca8c-481d-b7a8-9bdc5151352b?source=craigslist",
