        "geocode_query": "344 Westchester Sq N, Billings",
        "description": "QR Code Link to This Post 2 Bed, 1 Bath Duplex, Garage, Fenced Yard & Washer/Dryer 344 Westchester Sq N, Apt B, Billings, MT 59105 1400.00 / Month 2 BEDROOMS | 1 BATHROOMS Interested? Fill out this form : https://renter.turbotenant.com/general-prescreener/T3duZXI6MTE2MzE1NQ==?property=2617262&source=cl Have questions? Contact the Landlord : https://rental.turbotenant.com/p/344-westchester-sq-n-billings-mt-unit-apt-b/5afdd1a3-37a6-406d-a105-9d72a38655ca?source=craigslist Property Description: Welcome to this clean and well-maintained 2-bedroom, 1 bathroom lower-level duplex located in a quiet, established Billings neighborhood. This functional and spacious unit offers a comfortable layout with a large bathroom featuring a double vanity and direct access from the primary bedroom. The kitchen includes a refrigerator, oven/range, dishwasher, and plenty of cabinet space. A washer and dryer are also included for your convenience. Outside, enjoy a separately fenced yard and a dedicated detached single-car garage for parking and additional storage. Conveniently located within walking distance of Castle Rock Park and Sandstone Elementary School, this home is also just minutes from Lake Hills Golf Course, Castle Rock Middle School, and Lake Elmo. Features: • 2 Bedrooms, 1 Bathroom • Double Vanity Bathroom • Direct Bathroom Access from Primary Bedroom • Refrigerator, Oven/Range & Dishwasher Included • Washer & Dryer Included • Dedicated Single-Car Garage • Separately Fenced Yard • Quiet Residential Neighborhood • Walking Distance to Castle Rock Park & Sandstone Elementary • Minutes from Lake Hills Golf Course & Lake Elmo Rent: $1,400/month Utilities: • Landlord pays water, sewer, and garbage • Tenant responsible for electricity Additional Information: • No pets • No smoking Enjoy comfortable living in a great location with easy access to schools, parks, recreation, and everyday conveniences. Available July 1st. Property Type : Multi Family Pets : No Pet